                  Raily FAQ

                  Getting Started
                  What is the Raily App?
                  Raily is a pioneering dating app for train travelers. It integrates cutting-edge AI, AR, and gamification elements to create an immersive user experience. Connect with fellow travelers, earn unique NFTs, and enjoy intelligent cashback benefits.
                  How can I download the Raily App?
                  The Raily app is slated for release in Q2 2024, initially on iOS with an Android version to follow. To get early access, fill out the form on our website. Once approved, you'll receive instructions on downloading and installing the Raily app on your device.
                  AI Matchmaking
                  What is the Unique AI Visual Matchmaking feature in the Raily app?
                  This novel tool in Raily personalizes your matchmaking process. Simply upload photos of people you find attractive, and our AI will analyze these to understand your specific visual tastes and interests, refining your matches accordingly.
                  What does Deep Social Matchmaking do in Raily?
                  Deep Social Matchmaking uses sophisticated algorithms to dissect social media activities, creating a comprehensive psychological portrait of potential matches. This feature allows for deeper connections based on shared interests and values.
                  How does the Music Taste Matching feature work in Raily?
                  This feature blends your love for travel and music. Our AI technology analyzes your Spotify playlists to understand your musical preferences, matching you with individuals who share your taste in music.
                  AI Companions
                  What are AI Companions in the Raily app?
                  AI Companions in the Raily app are innovative features designed to enrich your journey by facilitating engaging and informative dialogues. These AI-powered chatbots cover various topics, from mental health support and relationship advice to nutritional guidance and astrology insights. Whether you're seeking company, advice, or learning opportunities during your travels, AI Companions ensure that you always have a conversation partner to make your journey more meaningful.
                  Token & Rewards
                  How does the $RLV token work?
                  Users can earn $RLV tokens for booking through Raily, leveling up, and completing quests. These tokens can be used to pay for various services within the Raily app and offer discounts with partners. Cashback in $RLV varies from 1% to 7% based on your level and booking type.
                  Where can I spend $RLV, and what are the benefits?
                  $RLV can be spent in various ways within the Raily platform. You can use it to activate premium features, send virtual gifts in private chats, boost your profile visibility, pay for KYC and enhanced profile verification, purchase travel NFTs from other members, and even contribute to charity. It's a versatile currency designed to enrich your Raily experience.
                  How can I earn and spend rewards in the Raily app?
                  Raily offers various quests and achievements that allow you to level up and increase your crypto cashback. Earned NFT cards can be gifted for discounts on services. You can also sell photos or videos on your profile for others to unlock using $RLV, with 80% of the income going to you.
                  Gamification
                  What is the leveling system in the Raily App?
                  The leveling system is a feature of the Raily App that encourages user engagement and rewards progress. As users level up, they can enjoy increased cashback, gifts, and unique quests and achievements.
                  How can I level up in the Raily App?
                  • Completing quests and achievements.
                  • Inviting friends to join the Raily App.
                  • Traveling actively with friends on trips.
                  • Visiting a certain number of cities or countries.
                  • Traveling a specified number of kilometers.
                  • Accumulating likes on chat messages and profiles.
                  • Having friends travel with you.
                  • Booking services via the Raily Buddy Concierge.
                  • Completing branded-promo quests/tasks. Participating in Charity quests.
                  What benefits do I get for leveling up?
                  As you level up, you unlock various benefits that can be activated using the $RLV token. These may include free boosts, gifts, or increased cash back. The higher your level, the more options become available.
                  How does leveling affect cashback and rewards?
                  Each level you achieve can lead to a cashback upgrade or the activation of special features. For example, at level 10, you can increase your cashback by +0.20% for X $RLV, and this activation lasts forever. At level 12, you can choose one free weekly "boost" forever for X $RLV. The exact rewards depend on the level attained and the options chosen by the user.
                  What's the role of the $RLV token in leveling?
                  The $RLV token is used to activate the exclusive options unlocked as users level up. Whether it's for activating free boosts, gifts, or increasing cashback, you'll need these tokens. The higher the level, the more options are available to be activated with the $RLV tokens.
                  Safety First
                  What steps does Raily take to ensure user safety?
                  Raily prioritizes user safety by offering banking-level KYC safety features for VIP users, including verification checks and background screenings. Remember, train stations and trains are high-security areas, and each ticket purchase can be tracked for additional safety.
                  How does the KYC process work?
                  Users will verify their identity through a secure Know Your Customer (KYC) process. After submitting identification documents and a selfie for authenticity checks, users can enjoy the Raily app with peace of mind, knowing all users are verified.
                  Future App Features
                  How does the AR/MR feature work and improve the user experience?
                  The AR/MR feature in Raily transforms your phone's camera or glasses into a target scanner. When launched, it scans the carriage and automatically identifies service users who match your preferences. This enhances the user experience by making it easier to find potential matches in real-time.
                  What is the purpose of the real-time translation feature?
                  The real-time translation feature is intended to break down language barriers that might exist between travel partners. It facilitates seamless communication between users who might not speak the same language, making connections easier.
                  How does Raily's AI Photo Advisor improve matches?
                  The AI Photo Advisor provides data-driven dating tips to enhance your app matches. It helps users understand how choosing appropriate photos and poses can increase their chances of successful matching.
                  How does AI Photographer work, and how does it enhance my profile?
                  The AI Photographer uses advanced technology, including Dall-E-2 and Stable Diffusion technology, to capture high-quality photos that truly represent who you are. It improves your profile by ensuring your pictures are not only attractive but also an authentic representation of your personality.
                  What is In-app travel insurance, and why should I consider it?
                  Raily's In-app travel insurance offers users the opportunity to stay protected while traveling. You can directly purchase insurance through the app for a worry-free journey. This feature is especially useful as it's based on a pay-as-you-travel model, so you only pay when you're actually traveling.
                  Features and Functions
                  What sets Raily apart?
                  Raily revolutionizes the dating experience by using AI technology for matchmaking. Our Unique AI Visual Matchmaking and Deep Social Matchmaking services understand your preferences and build a comprehensive psychological profile to improve matches. We also offer Music Taste Matching by analyzing your Spotify playlists. Alongside these, Raily introduces innovative features like AR explorations, real-time translation, AI-guided photo recommendations, travel insurance options, in-app payments, personalized relationship coaching, and compatibility assessments to ensure a captivatingjourney.
                  What new features are coming to the Raily app?
                  We're continually expanding our feature set. Soon, you'll be able to use your phone or AR glasses as a scanner to identify matching service users, access AI photography services for enhanced dating photos, and conveniently purchase travel insurance within the app.
                  Raily Buddy Concierge
                  What is the Raily Buddy in the Raily app?
                  Raily Buddy is an AI-powered reactive trip planner designed to provide users with tailor-made booking services during travels. Whether you're seeking hotels, museums, restaurants, taxis, or other accommodations, Raily Buddy adapts to your needs and preferences, enhancing your travel experience.
                  How does the Raily Buddy work?
                  Raily Buddy utilizes advanced AI technologies, including OpenAI GPT-4 and among others, for real-time analysis. By monitoring user chats and profile updates (with user consent), Raily Buddy dynamically adjusts its recommendations, ensuring they are personalized and relevant. In addition, it features voice tuning capabilities using Whisper GPT, allowing users to adjust recommendations verbally.
                  How does Raily Buddy enhance the user experience on Raily?
                  Raily Buddy significantly enhances user engagement by providing constant, personalized concierge services, not just during travels but also when planning and reminiscing. By ensuring that users have ready access to tailored booking services, Raily Buddy transforms the travel experience into a more seamless, enjoyable, and convenient process.
                  VIP membership
                  What additional benefits do I get with a VIP?
                  VIP members enjoy increased cashback rewards, chat message read confirmation, browsing in incognito mode, viewing who has liked or viewed their profile, response time of chat partners, a monthly Boost to increase profile visibility, AI-enhanced matchmaking, an ad-free experience, a special frame for their avatar, and access to unique emojis.
                  NFT & Gamification
                  How do NFTs work in Raily?
                  In Raily, NFTs (ERC-6651) are functional objects, not just visual ones. Earn travel-themed NFT stamps of iconic landmarks from visited cities or send AIdesigned digital greeting cards to friends and family. Trade these NFTs with other Raily members to earn cash and get discounts.
                  How do I earn and use NFTs in Raily?
                  Users can earn NFTs through purchases or as rewards. The rarity of NFTs influences the discounts and bonuses available when booking services in respective cities.
                  What benefits do I get from collecting NFTs?
                  Collecting NFTs unlocks various discounts and bonuses when booking services. They serve as travel souvenirs, are tradable and offer unique capabilities like carbon offsetting, adding a unique touch to your Raily experience.
                  How does the Travel-to-Earn NFT feature work?
                  A: Complete certain travel milestones to earn unique NFTs. These NFTs are functional objects with unique capabilities that provide bonuses and discounts. For example, you could earn a rare NFT by attending Oktoberfest in Munich, which provides a 2% cashback on restaurant bookings.
                  Raily Master Friendship
                  What is the Raily Master Program?
                  • The Raily Master Program is a referral initiative for Raily users to invite friends to the App, allowing them to earn rewards and benefits.
                  • Instant Rewards: When you invite a friend who joins the App, you receive $RLV tokens that can be used to activate a Premium account and access otherfeatures.
                  • Group Achievements: When you travel with friends, you can activate group achievements to earn $RLV rewards for completing shared tasks, like coveringspecific distances or visiting various cities.
                  • Individual Bonuses: You earn bonuses and XP for every kilometer your friend travels within the app, even if you are not traveling together. Upon reachingcertain distances, you can unlock friend achievements and quests to earn rewards such as $RLV, XP, and discount coupons.
                  • Cashback: You receive a percentage of your friend's in-app payments as $RLV cashback.
                  Is there a limit to how much I can earn in the Raily Master Program?
                  No, the more friends you invite, the more rewards you can earn. Every friend contributes to your rewards, whether through instant rewards, group achievements, individual bonuses, or cashback. You will see all the rewards you've earned from your friends in a dedicated area within the App.
                  Charity
                  How does Raily support charity?
                  Raily encourages members to protect the environment. Completing achievements and quests can trigger donations (funded by us) to a cause of your choice, and you'll receive a digital certificate confirming your contribution.
                  How can I participate in Charity events, and what benefits do I get from this?
                  Participate in charity events by completing various achievements and quests within Raily. Once completed, a donation is triggered to a chosen cause. In return, you receive a digital certificate confirming your contribution while supporting environmental protection causes: Plastic Cleanup, Planting Trees, Saving Sea Turtles, Marine Protection Area, Protecting land for wildlife, Restoring coral reefs.
                  App Privacy
                  Can I trust the security of your app?
                  Absolutely! Safety comes first for us. We employ cutting-edge technology to safeguard your personal information and create a secure online environment. Our robust security framework ensures encryption, authentication, and dataprivacy, providing a secure and trustworthy platform.

                  We have a multitude of security measures in place:

                  Data Encryption: We use end-to-end encryption (E2EE) and SSL/TLS to protect your data.

                  Authentication: We use two-factor authentication (2FA) and OAuth 2.0 to ensure that only you can access your account.

                  Data Storage: Our databases are encrypted and we use secure cloud storage providers.

                  Backend Infrastructure: Our backend infrastructure, which depends onproduct needs, is hosted in AWS, Microsoft Azure, and Google Cloud. It is fully monitored to detect any downtime.

                  Third-Party Risk Management: We work with trusted third parties like AmazonAWS, Google Cloud, and Microsoft Azure.

                  Machine Learning & AI: We rigorously vet our systems and have secure APIintegrations with industry leaders like Microsoft and Google.

                  User Verification: We use advanced machine learning algorithms and neuralnetworks provided by OpenAI for user verification. In addition, we utilize modern ML developments such as LLAMA2, Antrophic Claude, and others toenhance our verification process.

                  Encrypted Chats: All chats are encrypted. The option for a Know YourCustomer (KYC) procedure is available voluntarily or to premium accountholders (verification provider Synaps). All KYC-passed accounts are markedwith a corresponding check. However, by default, our AI/neural networksattempt to vet users to the best of their ability.

                  Encryption Standards: We use AES and RSA encryption standards, alongsidethe Double Ratchet Algorithm for additional security.
                  How do you handle my location data?
                  The check-in procedure (ticket scanning) always verifies your willingness to disclose your presence and your seat location. By default, no one knows aboutyou unless you decide otherwise. We respect your privacy and give you controlover your data. Lets jump more in details, because its very important to us:

                  Disclosure Settings: You always have the option to disclose whether you're onthe train. Your routes and location on the train are completely within yourcontrol. All the information you share with others is up to you. We do not takeresponsibility for your actions and the information you choose to share. Bydefault, the app's settings are set to full confidentiality!

                  Visibility: However, you should remember that with the visibility setting turned off, no one will be able to find you. Your existence will simply be unknown toeveryone, which is logical.

                  GPS Activation: To ensure that you're discoverable on the train and to verifythat you've correctly checked in (and not a fake user or bot), we'll ask you toactivate geolocation which will only work within the declared distance of yourtrip, occasionally checking your presence on the train - we primarily do this atthe moment of passing by any of the stations on your route. If you turn offgeolocation mode, you will be unavailable for anyone to search for on your train.This way, we protect our community from bots that may claim to be on the trainbut aren't.
                  ‍
                  Active Geolocation in Your City: If you are already in your city, activegeolocation is required for you to comfortably use the AI Buddy Conciergeservices and to be available for others to search. You can choose to beunavailable for acquaintances, but still use the Concierge service.
                  Is my conversation on the app secure?
                  Yes, all your chats are encrypted. We have put in place advanced verification processes to ensure that your conversations stay private and secure.
                  What if I find a security vulnerability in the Raily App?
                  If you believe you have discovered a vulnerability within Raily App, please submit a report to us by emailing security@raily.app. We do not participate in a public bug bounty program at this time, nor do we provide monetary rewards for publicly reported findings
                  What if I believe my account has been compromised?
                  If you believe your account has been compromised or you are seeing suspicious activity on your account, please report it to us at security@raily.app. Your trust is our top priority. We're committed to keeping your data safe and
                  secure.
